data.description: Welcome to San Carlos Park.  This house is located perfectly near everything, shopping, dining, airport, and entertainment.  There are granite countertops in the open kitchen.  Large family room, and all bedrooms are oversized.  There's plenty of room for a pool.  The landscaping provides excellent privacy without a fence.  Roof is only 4 years old, and the AC system was just replaced.  This is a great first time home, or for an investment property.
